SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR SOLUTION $PAR
(a) \(F($a)=\int^{$a}_{$a} $f\;dt=0\).
$PAR
(b) \(F'(x)=\displaystyle \frac{d}{dx}\int^{x}_{$a} $f\;dt=$F\;\), \(\;F'($a)=$Fa\).

$PAR
(b) \(F''(x)= \frac{d}{dx} \left[$F\right]=$G\;\), \(\;F''($a)=$Ga\).
